NAME

  **file** - output filetype information


SYNOPSIS

    file *filename* 

DESCRIPTION

    File will output the file type for a given file. Directories will output 
    `directory`, and any webfiles will provide information about their 
    file type and encoding.  

OPTIONS

  -h, --help:  output usage information and exit

SEE ALSO

    [cat](/data/man/cat.dsmd), [dsmdbrowser](/data/man/dsmdbrowser.dsmd), [imgview](/data/man/imgview.dsmd)